description: Done to the 9's! Do people still say that?? Well its appropriate here! Impeccable stye, top of the line everything and no detail overlooked. Check out that kitchen! High-end Bertazonni kitchen appliance package with beautiful quartz countertops that run up the backsplash (nice touch!), handsome two-tone Italian cabinetry, paneled dishwasher, drawer microwave, and a stainless steel hood vent. The bathrooms are stunning. Beautiful tile and fixtures, deep soaking tub in the master bath, even state of the art mirrors. Don't miss the built out closets, in unit washer and dryer, tankless, energy efficient water heater and in unit storage area. Built in 2021, this like new 1 bed, 1.5 bath sits in a prime city point location just a few blocks from the beach yet walkable to many bars and restaurants. The best of both worlds! Come and see this beauty today.
